body:
I commented this in another thread [here](https://ruqqus.com/post/1430/young-white-mother-killed-by-black/3c4p), but I'll share since it's about the same topic:

The event itself seems well documented, yet for some reason there is not any other mainstream coverage on this. I checked all the usual screaming news websites, but it was only picked up by right leaning ones. Hm, I wonder why.

Some takeaways -

- The mother was out with her Fiancee, they encountered the group of BLM supporters and got into an argument
- They actually left and went separate ways
- A few minutes later, the BLM group shot, and the Fiancee shot back
- Mother was the only casualty, a GoFundMe has been started to fund for her funeral & kid
